{"tid":2004261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疑心台灣也有「黑警」 港生隔海爆料扯出性侵案","createTime":"2020-05-06T10:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T03:46:21.000Z","uid":32148,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4501321b27e56e24f600114ad1cdb211a4e713bd","tid":2004261,"uid":32148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"反送中來台尋求「庇護」的香港籍馬姓學生，因涉嫌性侵港女同學遭法辦，但據指出，檢警前往馬的宿舍搜索時，原本保密低調沒有張揚，但其他香港學生不明所以，以為台灣也有「黑警」，質疑他們為何要搜索學生寢室，竟然暗裝密錄器搜證，還將照片火速傳給香港媒體「爆料」，最後才導致這起性侵案曝光。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，涉案的馬姓學生因為參與「反送中」，身份非常敏感，台灣檢警在偵辦時十分低調，但他們前往馬生宿舍查看時，其他香港學生，竟以為台灣可能也有「黑警」，於是使用秘錄器，拍下檢警的搜索過程，並在第一時間傳給香港媒體，聲稱：「我們在台灣的學生宿舍，也被警察搜索了！」懷疑有政治成份存在。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是港媒率先披露檢警搜查照片，但也循線查出，全案竟是由馬姓學生性侵女同學而起，整個案件才隨之曝光。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200506000078-260402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20200506000078-260402&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=cc38af1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200506000078-260402</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恕我直言喇，有d 大/中學雞真係好撚蠢，上晒腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a10757c1acc5243d00f8ea2abf6dc6218476b6d","tid":2004261,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"黑警又屈手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9eb8eb2b5528c6fd89e01e3da1560f71f7a19eb","tid":2004261,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:33:16.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"57670766bb64726f713a1508d0b